701#define LSI_STARTUP_TIME 85U
710/******************************************************************************/
711/* Peripheral Registers_Bits_Definition */
712/******************************************************************************/
713
714/******************************************************************************/
715/* */
716/* CRC calculation unit (CRC) */
717/* */
718/******************************************************************************/
719
720/******************* Bit definition for CRC_DR register *********************/
721#define CRC_DR_DR_Pos (0U)
722#define CRC_DR_DR_Msk (0xFFFFFFFFUL << CRC_DR_DR_Pos)
723#define CRC_DR_DR CRC_DR_DR_Msk
725/******************* Bit definition for CRC_IDR register ********************/
726#define CRC_IDR_IDR_Pos (0U)
727#define CRC_IDR_IDR_Msk (0xFFUL << CRC_IDR_IDR_Pos)
728#define CRC_IDR_IDR CRC_IDR_IDR_Msk
730/******************** Bit definition for CRC_CR register ********************/
731#define CRC_CR_RESET_Pos (0U)
732#define CRC_CR_RESET_Msk (0x1UL << CRC_CR_RESET_Pos)
733#define CRC_CR_RESET CRC_CR_RESET_Msk
735/******************************************************************************/
736/* */
737/* Power Control */
738/* */
739/******************************************************************************/
740
741/******************** Bit definition for PWR_CR register ********************/
742#define PWR_CR_LPDS_Pos (0U)
743#define PWR_CR_LPDS_Msk (0x1UL << PWR_CR_LPDS_Pos)
744#define PWR_CR_LPDS PWR_CR_LPDS_Msk
745#define PWR_CR_PDDS_Pos (1U)
746#define PWR_CR_PDDS_Msk (0x1UL << PWR_CR_PDDS_Pos)
747#define PWR_CR_PDDS PWR_CR_PDDS_Msk
748#define PWR_CR_CWUF_Pos (2U)
749#define PWR_CR_CWUF_Msk (0x1UL << PWR_CR_CWUF_Pos)
750#define PWR_CR_CWUF PWR_CR_CWUF_Msk
751#define PWR_CR_CSBF_Pos (3U)
752#define PWR_CR_CSBF_Msk (0x1UL << PWR_CR_CSBF_Pos)
753#define PWR_CR_CSBF PWR_CR_CSBF_Msk
754#define PWR_CR_PVDE_Pos (4U)
755#define PWR_CR_PVDE_Msk (0x1UL << PWR_CR_PVDE_Pos)
756#define PWR_CR_PVDE PWR_CR_PVDE_Msk
758#define PWR_CR_PLS_Pos (5U)
759#define PWR_CR_PLS_Msk (0x7UL << PWR_CR_PLS_Pos)
760#define PWR_CR_PLS PWR_CR_PLS_Msk
761#define PWR_CR_PLS_0 (0x1UL << PWR_CR_PLS_Pos)
762#define PWR_CR_PLS_1 (0x2UL << PWR_CR_PLS_Pos)
763#define PWR_CR_PLS_2 (0x4UL << PWR_CR_PLS_Pos)
766#define PWR_CR_PLS_LEV0 0x00000000U
767#define PWR_CR_PLS_LEV1 0x00000020U
768#define PWR_CR_PLS_LEV2 0x00000040U
769#define PWR_CR_PLS_LEV3 0x00000060U
770#define PWR_CR_PLS_LEV4 0x00000080U
771#define PWR_CR_PLS_LEV5 0x000000A0U
772#define PWR_CR_PLS_LEV6 0x000000C0U
773#define PWR_CR_PLS_LEV7 0x000000E0U
775/* Legacy defines */
776#define PWR_CR_PLS_2V2 PWR_CR_PLS_LEV0
777#define PWR_CR_PLS_2V3 PWR_CR_PLS_LEV1
778#define PWR_CR_PLS_2V4 PWR_CR_PLS_LEV2
779#define PWR_CR_PLS_2V5 PWR_CR_PLS_LEV3
780#define PWR_CR_PLS_2V6 PWR_CR_PLS_LEV4
781#define PWR_CR_PLS_2V7 PWR_CR_PLS_LEV5
782#define PWR_CR_PLS_2V8 PWR_CR_PLS_LEV6
783#define PWR_CR_PLS_2V9 PWR_CR_PLS_LEV7
784
785#define PWR_CR_DBP_Pos (8U)
786#define PWR_CR_DBP_Msk (0x1UL << PWR_CR_DBP_Pos)
787#define PWR_CR_DBP PWR_CR_DBP_Msk
790/******************* Bit definition for PWR_CSR register ********************/
791#define PWR_CSR_WUF_Pos (0U)
792#define PWR_CSR_WUF_Msk (0x1UL << PWR_CSR_WUF_Pos)
793#define PWR_CSR_WUF PWR_CSR_WUF_Msk
794#define PWR_CSR_SBF_Pos (1U)
795#define PWR_CSR_SBF_Msk (0x1UL << PWR_CSR_SBF_Pos)
796#define PWR_CSR_SBF PWR_CSR_SBF_Msk
797#define PWR_CSR_PVDO_Pos (2U)
798#define PWR_CSR_PVDO_Msk (0x1UL << PWR_CSR_PVDO_Pos)
799#define PWR_CSR_PVDO PWR_CSR_PVDO_Msk
800#define PWR_CSR_EWUP_Pos (8U)
801#define PWR_CSR_EWUP_Msk (0x1UL << PWR_CSR_EWUP_Pos)
802#define PWR_CSR_EWUP PWR_CSR_EWUP_Msk
804/******************************************************************************/
805/* */
806/* Backup registers */
807/* */
808/******************************************************************************/
809
810/******************* Bit definition for BKP_DR1 register ********************/
811#define BKP_DR1_D_Pos (0U)
812#define BKP_DR1_D_Msk (0xFFFFUL << BKP_DR1_D_Pos)
